snippet.title: Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel! The Moon Dance Trailer!
snippet.description:
Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel blasts off on October 14, 2014 in North America and on October 17, 2014 worldwide, for the Xbox 360, PlayStation 3, and Windows PC. Experience low-gravity gunplay on Pandora's moon with four new vault hunters and a whole new campaign. Pre-order now and unlock access to the Shock Drop Slaughter Pit bonus content at: http://bit.ly/1xbQxWQ

Hit the 'Subscribe' button to stay up to date on the latest videos!
